    "Although possible, some exciting documentation exists on using LLM in developing digital learning ecosystems [116].Initially, the tool was designed to assist teachers and educators by providing timely advice, answers to everyday questions, and guidance on frequently asked questions.",
    "Based on existing research, the LLM has many benefits for teachers.",
    "In particular, it provides personalized learning support by allowing students to adapt resources and activities to meet their needs.",
    "Also, teachers can use LLM to match course objectives, learning outcomes, and standards [117].",
    "Figure 13 illustrates the opportunities for using LLMs in higher education."
